Class FactsChanged

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jeasy.rules.api.Facts
      • fr.sorbonne_u.alasca.easyrules.extensions.FactsChanged
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.util.Map.Entry<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>>

    public class FactsChanged
extends org.jeasy.rules.api.Facts
    The class FactsChanged extends the class Facts from the Easy Rules library to record in a more efficient way the facts that have been changed after firing the rules on the set of facts; this eases programming inferences until no more facts are changed or added to the set of facts.
